Quest:All's Well

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
Show of Strength

Given By: Olemeeli Thornpaw

Giver Location: Savannah
This is a storyline quest.

Goals:
Collect 3 Well Stones
Repair Well
Talk to Olemeeli Thornpaw
Hand In: Olemeeli Thornpaw

Reward:

190
5,340


Leads to:

Open Cages (storyline quest)
Better Mousetrap (side quest)

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to All's Well should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.

Search for content related to All's Well in the Central Wiki Forums by clicking here.
